data.eml:eml: Annotated checklist of freshwater fishes from Brunei Darussalam, Borneo

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal volume Sulaiman, Zohrah, Hui, Tan Heok, Lim, Kelvin Kok Peng (2018): Annotated checklist of freshwater fishes from Brunei Darussalam, Borneo. Zootaxa 4379 (1), DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4379.1.2
